{"tid":1599050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柒婆公然違反基本法 係公開對話中直認無高度自治","createTime":"2019-09-27T18:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T18:34:34.000Z","uid":258450,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0896a0fb091c81d4d6a26a60abfe7462a22bbac2","tid":1599050,"uid":258450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:14:04.000Z","msg":"文宣核彈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要整埋圖<br />\n英文版推上國際<br />\n香港特首公然違反基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好俾佢PR呃以為有對話出路，極權不嬲都係意見接受態度照舊<br />\n繼續進行文宣，繼續抗爭，繼際國際戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柒婆公開對話中言論重點：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iUJZfhDalkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiUJZfhDalkg&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjwmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=038e204e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iUJZfhDalkg</a><br />\n<br />\n1:57:30－40<br />\n林鄭:「如果香港要保持一國兩制，唔係香港自治，對唔住; <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自治就唔係一國兩制</span></span></strong>。所以我希望喺喱度要講清楚，我哋要有底線。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭言論違反了基本法。<br />\n《基本法》第二條: 「全國人民代表大會授權香港特別行政區依照本法的規定<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">實行高度自治</span></strong></span>，享有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">管理權、立法權、獨立的司法權和終審權</span></strong></span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8mL0pMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8mL0pMA.jpg&h=a54e46ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1fr4MB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1fr4MB.jpg&h=bc6df319&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"749e87fdfa2d3d13294700fdffce4a3ff970cb59","tid":1599050,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"